data.description: Motivated Seller offers you luxury country living in the hills of Central Texas on the Lampasas River! Personal private resort-like property ISO new owner! Seller offers closing cost assistance, interest rate buy down, 1 yr HOA fees, and home warranty.The main house is perched on a 10.72 acre lot within a gated community off Hwy 195. Scenic views of rolling hills, 18,000 gallon swimming pool, basketball/pickleball court, Guest House/Workshop with electricity and full bath, also a fenced chicken yard with coop!  Upon entry of the main house you will see the formal living and dining room leading into the large office space, all overlooking the pool and court area. A beautiful decorative stone wood-burning fireplace centers the wall. The eat-in-kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a stone backsplash with custom cabinetry. French doors allow natural light from the back patio area. Completing the first floor you will also find a utility/laundry room with additional shelving, a guest bedroom, and full bath. The second floor is where you will find the family room, primary bedroom with a spa-like bath, and three additional minor bedrooms. Doors from the primary bedroom and family room access the balcony area which provides you with ample space to relax and enjoy coffee or wine while taking in the stunning countryside views. The minor bath upstairs has a single vanity with dual sinks. Other amenities within this personal property include a detached guest house/workshop with electricity, paved driveways, RV parking, fluctuating creek front at the back of the property, multiple outdoor sitting areas with pergolas and petrified rock retaining walls. This property is located in an HOA giving residents access to three Riverside Park areas and walking/horse trails at only $570 per year. Looking for a second property to just get away from it all? This property is it! Thirty minutes north of Round Rock. About an hour north of downtown Austin.
